response.overview: The 41st edition of Saturday Night's Main Event is an upcoming professional wrestling television special produced by the World Wrestling Federation (WWF). As the name implies, it will be the 41st Saturday Night's Main Event special overall and it will take place on Saturday October 25, 2025, at the Arena CDMX, officially the Mexico City Arena, in Azcapotzalco, Mexico City, Mexico.
response.title: Saturday Night's Main Event XLI
